QuestData.Title: Mung-Mung's Vote II: Rotten to the Core
QuestData.Description: Dem virmen's back!$B$BThey been biting Mr. Mudclaw's carrots. Ruining his crop. And who is gonna pay? Mung-Mung, that's who!$B$BYou go get the chewed up carrots before Mr. Mudclaw sees. They all over the fields to the southwest, and down under the ground in the virmen's tunnels, too.$B$BOtherwise, Mung-Mung in big trouble.$B$BYou do this for me?
